snippet.title: Cerulean Trailer [SuNoFes 2015]
snippet.description:
Cerulean is a short visual novel by Pink Pomeranian Parade, created for SuNoFes 2015 (https://itch.io/jam/sunofes).
Cerulean is available for Mac, Windows, and Linux @ itch.io: http://laniessa.itch.io/cerulean

Song Credits - "Take Me To The Sky":
Sebastian Woodland - Composition/Arrangement
RikuRikuRi - Vocals
Laiska & Tenshio - Lyrics

Video Credits:
RouFleur - Video editing
Tenshio - Character art
Laniessa - Background art
Laiska - Text
